description:
This is a 34 minute workout called '30 MIN KILLER STRENGTH Workout - With Weights - Home Workout with Dumbbells' from the channel growingannanas.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging and Moderate.
